==English==

===Suffix===
'''-o''' (''plural'' '''-os''' or '''-oes''', depending on the word)
#(''used especially in Australia'') A [[diminutive]] suffix.

====Usage notes====
*'''-o''' is generally applied to nouns, but sometimes adjectives, like '''[[agro]]'''

